headline.main: Hoard of Coins Extracted From Sea Turtle
headline.print_headline: Hoard of Coins Extracted From Sea Turtle

lead_paragraph: Thai veterinarians on Monday removed 915 coins from a 25-year-old sea turtle which had been swallowing items thrown into her pool for good luck, eventually limiting her ability to swim.
